Rating: 4
With only two modifications, this is a 4-forker: (1) I added thinly sliced red onion to the peppers and sauteed on very low heat for about an hour, which makes them silky and more delicious, and (2) instead of breasts, I used thighs because they are juicier and don't dry out. Served this dish over polenta. Wow! Next time, I might add a splash of balsamic vinegar.

